        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1710924187" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3104193343051591373">I read <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/38154.Orlando_Furioso' title='Orlando Furioso by Ludovico Ariosto' rel='nofollow noopener'>Orlando Furioso</a> many years ago, but I still remember the good feeling as I went through <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/21460.Ludovico_Ariosto' title='Ludovico Ariosto' rel='nofollow noopener'>Ludovico Ariosto</a>&apos;s pages. A fantastic and unusual parody of chivalry. <br/><i>
  <blockquote>“Nature made him, and then broke the mold.” <br/><br/>“Ah, how I rue that what I could have done I did not do!”</blockquote>
</i>Highly recommended!<br/>___</span>
  <span id="freeText3104193343051591373" style="display:none">I read <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/38154.Orlando_Furioso" title="Orlando Furioso by Ludovico Ariosto" rel="nofollow noopener">Orlando Furioso</a> many years ago, but I still remember the good feeling as I went through <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/21460.Ludovico_Ariosto" title="Ludovico Ariosto" rel="nofollow noopener">Ludovico Ariosto</a>'s pages. A fantastic and unusual parody of chivalry. <br /><i>
  <blockquote>“Nature made him, and then broke the mold.” <br /><br />“Ah, how I rue that what I could have done I did not do!”</blockquote>
</i>Highly recommended!<br />___</span>
