<span id="freeTextContainer3212341970200217143">A magical experience!<br/><br/>this has to be one of my top 10 favorite books. <br/><br/>The writing is genius, I love how Ariosto always gets you hooked! <br/>and how he combines different genres together and not to mention surprise us with all these twists and turns!<br/><br/>The wonderful Ruggiero, who is brave and noble, how I loved his flight to Alcina&apos;s island! <br/><br/>and of course great Rinaldo and his conquests in Scotland! <br/><br/>This is is like Lord of the Rings, Harry potter and Homer all in one. <br/><br/>Beautiful, with sub stories too! <br/><br/>You</span>
  <span id="freeText3212341970200217143" style="display:none">A magical experience!<br /><br />this has to be one of my top 10 favorite books. <br /><br />The writing is genius, I love how Ariosto always gets you hooked! <br />and how he combines different genres together and not to mention surprise us with all these twists and turns!<br /><br />The wonderful Ruggiero, who is brave and noble, how I loved his flight to Alcina's island! <br /><br />and of course great Rinaldo and his conquests in Scotland! <br /><br />This is is like Lord of the Rings, Harry potter and Homer all in one. <br /><br />Beautiful, with sub stories too! <br /><br />You can trace back many fantasy films and other writings to this book right here. </span>
