      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1161788-orlando-furioso">Quotes from Orlando Furioso</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
